===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# (''often capitalized'') The sole natural [[satellite]] of the [[Earth]], represented in astronomy and astrology by [[☾]].
# Any substantially sized natural satellite of a planet.
# (''literary'') A month, particularly a lunar month.
#: ''many moons ago''

